**1. Executive Summary**
The True Agentic Commerce Architecture decouples conversational UI from enterprise business logic by utilizing a Supervisor-Worker Paradigm.
Instead of relying on a single monolithic LLM prompt, this system uses LangGraph as a stateful orchestrator that delegates complex tasks to highly specialized CrewAI Swarms. These swarms communicate via strict A2A (Agent-to-Agent) JSON protocols and execute actions securely against the Snowflake Data Cloud using the Model Context Protocol (MCP).

**2. Core Technology Stack**
Experience Layer: Streamlit (Multi-Modal Voice + Chat, Dynamic UI generation).

State & Governance (The Supervisor): LangGraph (Manages session memory, routing, and Human-in-the-Loop checkpoints).

Agentic Collaboration (The Workers): CrewAI (Creates specialized agent crews that debate and collaborate to solve sub-tasks).

Integration Standard: Model Context Protocol (MCP) servers (Provides a standardized, secure bridge to enterprise APIs).

Data Lakehouse: Snowflake (Customer 360, Live Inventory, Order Management).

**3. High-Level System Architecture**
This diagram illustrates how the experience layer routes through the LangGraph Supervisor, which then orchestrates the CrewAI swarms. The swarms exclusively interact with enterprise data via the standardized MCP layer.


graph TD
    %% Define Styles
    classDef ui fill:#f9f6fa,stroke:#d6b4fc,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef orchestrator fill:#e6f2ff,stroke:#6baed6,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef crew fill:#e2f0cb,stroke:#8bd346,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef mcp fill:#ffe6cc,stroke:#ffb347,stroke-width:2px;
    classDef data fill:#f4f4f8,stroke:#a6a6a6,stroke-width:2px;

    subgraph Client [Experience Layer]
        UI[Streamlit Multi-Modal UI<br/>Voice / Text / Dynamic Widgets]:::ui
    end

    subgraph Orchestration [LangGraph Orchestrator]
        SM[Supervisor Node<br/>Intent Routing & State Memory]:::orchestrator
        HITL[Governance Checkpoint<br/>Manager Approval Node]:::orchestrator
    end

    subgraph Swarms [CrewAI Specialized Swarms]
        SC[Sales & Discovery Crew<br/>Agents: Concierge, Upseller]:::crew
        RC[Fulfillment Recovery Crew<br/>Agents: Inventory Analyst, Margin Calculator]:::crew
        LC[Post-Purchase Crew<br/>Agents: Policy Enforcer, Logistics Sentinel]:::crew
    end

    subgraph Integration [MCP Protocol Layer]
        MCPS[Snowflake MCP Server]:::mcp
        MCPE[ERP / Payment MCP Server]:::mcp
        MCPSL[Slack / Comms MCP Server]:::mcp
    end

    subgraph Enterprise [Data Platform]
        SNOW[(Snowflake Data Cloud)]:::data
        ERP[(External ERP)]:::data
    end

    %% Connections
    UI <-->|User Input / UI Render| SM
    SM -->|Delegate via A2A Protocol| SC
    SM -->|Delegate via A2A Protocol| RC
    SM -->|Delegate via A2A Protocol| LC
    
    SC & RC & LC <-->|Execute Tools| Integration
    
    MCPS <-->|Live Queries| SNOW
    MCPE <-->|Transactions| ERP
    
    RC -.->|Triggers Pause| HITL
    HITL -.->|Resume Execution| RC


**4. The Agentic Flow (A2A Collaboration & Resolution) **
The High-Impact Demo Scenario: A VIP B2B customer wants to order 50 laptops for a new office. The primary warehouse only has 30. Instead of failing the order, the LangGraph Supervisor wakes up the Fulfillment Recovery Crew.

The Inventory Analyst Agent finds 20 laptops in a secondary warehouse.

The Logistics Agent calculates a $500 expedited shipping fee to combine them.

The Margin Calculator Agent checks the customer's Platinum status and agrees to absorb the $500 fee to save a $100,000 deal.

Before finalizing, it hits the LangGraph HITL Checkpoint for the Account Executive to click "Approve."

Sequence Diagram: Agent-to-Agent (A2A) Collaboration


sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant LG as LangGraph Supervisor
    box rgb(226, 240, 203) CrewAI: Fulfillment Recovery Swarm
        participant IA as Inventory Agent
        participant MA as Margin Agent
    end
    participant MCP as MCP Layer (Snowflake)
    participant UI as Streamlit UI (HITL)

    User->>LG: "I need 50 Apex M5 Laptops for the new branch."
    LG->>LG: Update State (Intent: Bulk Order)
    LG->>IA: Delegate Task (JSON Payload: sku=APEX-1001, qty=50)
    
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over IA, MCP: A2A Data Gathering
        IA->>MCP: check_inventory(sku=APEX-1001)
        MCP-->>IA: {"WH-1": 30, "WH-2": 20}
        IA->>MA: A2A Message: "Split shipment required. Extra logistics cost: $500. Advise."
        MA->>MCP: get_customer_profile(customer_id)
        MCP-->>MA: {"tier": "Platinum", "LTV": "$500k"}
        MA->>IA: A2A Message: "Customer is Platinum. Absorb the $500 cost to save the margin."
    end

    IA->>LG: Return Resolution Plan (JSON: Absorb cost, split ship)
    
    LG->>UI: ⚠️ HITL PAUSE: Margin Exception Detected
    Note over User, UI: Manager reviews the CrewAI debate log in the UI.
    User->>UI: Clicks "Approve Override"
    UI->>LG: Resume execution
    
    LG->>MCP: process_payment() & create_order()
    LG-->>User: Render Rich Cart UI & Confirmation message


**5. Why this Architecture Wins (Talking Points for the Panel)**
When you present this architecture to the Salesforce panel, focus on these three pillars:

True Agentic Collaboration (CrewAI + LangGraph): "Salesforce Agentforce is excellent for single-agent tasks. But enterprise commerce requires debate. By nesting CrewAI within LangGraph, we enable agents with conflicting goals (e.g., an Inventory Agent trying to ship fast vs. a Margin Agent trying to save money) to debate and find the optimal business outcome before presenting it to the user."

Standardized Integration (MCP): "We don't write custom API wrappers for every LLM. By using the Model Context Protocol (MCP), our Snowflake data and ERP systems become instantly securely discoverable by any agent in the swarm."

Controllable Autonomy (HITL): "We leverage LangGraph's state machine to inject Human-in-the-Loop checkpoints. The AI swarm has the autonomy to solve the out-of-stock puzzle, but enterprise governance dictates a human must approve margin exceptions. This is responsible AI."
